'''Willy Ndahiro''' ni Umunya[[rwanda]] wavukiye i [[bujumbura]] ,[[Burundi]] iya 1, mata 1976, wamenyekanye nka Paul muri filimi nyarwanda yakunzwe  cyane <nowiki>''Ikigeragezo cy' ubuzima", Ni umuyobozi ndetse n'</nowiki>umukinnyi wa filimi nyarwanda kuva 2006<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/filmmaker-ndahiro-unveils-new-film-production-studio</ref>.<ref>http://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/willy-ndahiro-agiye-gusohora-filime-igaragaramo-umuhanzi-ngarambe-francois</ref>  Byatumye aba umuyobozi wa komite ishinze abakinnyi bamafilimi mu [[Rwanda]] umwanya amazeho imyaka irenga 10<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/70010/umukinnyi-wa-filime-willy-ndahiro-aramaganira-kure-ibihuha-b-70010.html</ref>. zimwe muri filimi yayoboye akanakinamo ni "Ay'urukundo"," Kanyarwanda","Anitha" na "Igisubizo cy'ubuzima".<ref>https://genesisbizz.com/Willy-Ndahiro-yagizwe-umuyobozi-mukuru-wa-Rwanda-Film-Federation-w-agateganyo</ref>

== Ubuzima bwa Willy muri make ==
Willy Ndahiro yavukiye mu [[Burundi]] muri 1976, muri 1993 yaje mu Rwanda yinjira mu gisirikare cya Rwanda Patriotic Army aatanya n'abandi guhagarika Genocide yakorewe abatutsi muri 1994,ubwo yakomereje akazi mu ngabo zirinda perezida kugeza 2004.<ref>https://rwanda.shafaqna.com/FR/AL/147647</ref> <ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/tea/rwanda-today/lifestyle/movie-industry-needs-more-money-1311272</ref>Willy avuye mu gisirikare yasubiye kwiga mu gihugu cy'uburundi aho yari yaracirkirije amashuri ye arangiriza mu bijyanye n'indimi(Lettre), muri 2006 nibwo yatangiye inzira yo gukina filimi atangirira kuri filimi yahise ituma amenyekana "Ikigeragezo cy'ubuzima"<ref>https://kglnews.com/index.php/tag/willy-ndahiro/</ref>, muri 2010 yayoboye ndetse akina muyindi filimi yakunzwe cyane "Ay'urukundo"<ref>https://umuseke.rw/paul-wo-mu-kigeragezo-cyubuzima-azabenguka-mushiki-we-muri-film-bazanyemo.html</ref>. Willy kandi yagiye ashinga studio zitunganya amafilimi harimo iyakoze filmi nyinshi yitwa"Vision Production Ltd"<ref>https://ibyamamare.com/ndahiro-natacha-umukobwa-ufite-amafoto-akunzwe-cyane-mbuga-nkoranyambaga-kubera-uburanga-bwe-agiye-gusohora-filime-yakinanye-na-musaza-we/</ref>

